'''Paricha''' was a soft-flavored spiced drink made from [[paricha root]]. Served warm, it had a pleasing, gentle aroma. During the [[Siege of Coruscant]], [[Leia Organa Solo/Legends|Leia Organa Solo]] feared that she might be having her last taste of paricha for a long time, as the root required to make it had to be imported from offworld.

